<title>rby ậjʿl</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ( rby ạ̹jʿl fy ṣlạty ḥyạẗ wkl ḥyạty ṣlạẗ
 ạ̉ṣly brwḥk wạ̹sẖbʿ rwḥy bṣwtk yạbn ạllh )2
 ( lmạ bạkwn jwh ạlrwḥ bḥyạ ạlsmwyạt
 qlby yfyḍ bạltsbyḥ wạsẖkr ʿ ạlbrkạt )2
 ( brkạt ạldm ạlly bndkẖl byh ạlạ̉qdạs
 wạlnʿmẗ ạlly tqwynạ wạ̹ymạn ạlkẖlạṣ )2
 ( ʿlmny ạzạy ạ̉qdm jsdy dẖbyḥẗ bkl kẖḍwʿ
 ạ̉ʿbd sẖkẖṣk rạfʿ ạ̹smk sạjd lk bkẖsẖwʿ )2
 ( kẖly sjwdy ykwn ljlạlk ṣmt wḥb wsẖwq
 wạmạ ạtklm ạ̉lqy̱ jmạlk ysby̱ ạlqlb lfwq )2
 (wạlạ̹sm ạlgẖạly ʿly ykwn fy lsạny ṣlạẗ
 wạlwqt ạ̹n mr ʿly yfwt kạllḥẓẗ mʿạh )2</lyrics>
</song>